				</div>
			</div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
				<img src="/products/waterio_1.webp" alt="1L Bottle" class="w-full h-48 object-contain">
				<div class="p-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Waterio Brand 1L Bottle</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Perfect for offices and travel</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
						<li>• Available in packs of 12</li>
						<li>• Durable BPA-free material</li>
						<li>• Easy-grip</li>
						<li>• Compatible with standard cupholders</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/products/waterio_1.webp" alt="500ml Bottles" class="w-full h-48 object-contain">
				<div class="p-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Waterio Brand 500 ml Bottles</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Ideal for retail and convenience stores</p>
