						<li>• Available in packs of 20</li>
						<li>• Recyclable PET bottles</li>
						<li>• Tamper-evident seals</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden text-center p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Coming Soon!</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We are excited to introduce:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                    <li>• Waterio - 200 ml</li>
                </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden text-center p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Coming Soon!</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We are excited to introduce:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                    <li>• 2 Litre Premium Bottle</li>
                </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden text-center p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Coming Soon!</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We are excited to introduce:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                    <li>• 1 Litre Premium Bottle</li>
                </ul>
      </div>

		</div>

		<div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-8 mb-16">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Bulk Orders & Custom Solutions</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Private Labeling</h3>
					<p class="mb-4">Create your own branded water bottles with our private labeling service. Minimum order quantities apply.</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
						<li>✓ Custom label design support</li>
						<li>✓ Multiple bottle size options</li>
						<li>✓ Flexible order quantities</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Wholesale Programs</h3>
					<p class="mb-4">Special pricing and support for bulk orders and regular supply contracts.</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
						<li>✓ Volume discounts</li>
						<li>✓ Dedicated account manager</li>
						<li>✓ Regular delivery schedules</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="text-center">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Order?</h2>
			<p class="mb-8">Contact our sales team to discuss your requirements and get a customized quote.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-blue-600">Get a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
